tale 750 S|Brutale 750 S]] (2002)}}\n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910 S|Brutale 910 S]] (2006)|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910 R|Brutale 910 R]] (2006)}}\n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 989 R|Brutale 989 R]] (2008)}}\n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 1078 RR|Brutale 1078 RR]] (2008)}}\n|-\n! colspan=4 | Limited edition models\n|-\n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 750 Oro|Brutale 750 Serie Oro]] (2002) [300 total]}}\n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910 R Italia|Brutale 910 R Italia]] (2006) [124 total]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910R Hydrogen|Brutale 910R Hydrogen]] (2007) [100 total]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910R Wally|Brutale 910 R Wally]]  (2008) [118 total]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910R Starfighter|Brutale 910R Starfighter]]  (2008) [99 total]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 910R Starfighter Titanium|Brutale 910R Starfighter Titanium]]  (2008) [23 total]}}\n| \n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale 1078 RR Jean Richard|Brutale 1078 RR Jean Richard]] (2008)}}\n|-\n! colspan=4 | CRC limited edition kits\n|-\n| {{bulleted list |[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale America|Brutale America]] (2005) [SP-05 (basic) - 300 total / SP-06 (full options) - 300 total]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale CRC|Brutale CRC]] (2005) [SP-07 (basic) - 300 total / SP-08 (full options) - 300 total]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale Mamba|Brutale Mamba]] (2006) [SP-09 (basic) - 300 total / SP-10 (full options) - 300 total / SP-11 (standard)]|[[MV Agusta Brutale series#Brutale Gladio|Brutale Gladio]] (2006) [SP-12 (basic) - 300 total / SP-13 (full options) - 300 total]}}\n| \n| \n| \n|}\n\n[[File:MV Agusta Brutale 1090 Special Edition \"Corse\" (10760160763).jpg|thumb|2013 MV Agusta Brutale 1090 RR Corse]]\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 |Second generation\n|-\n! 920 cc !! 1,000 cc !! 1,078 cc\n|-\n! colspan=3 |Produ